inn1.comm: starts with a length ball outside off, the ball is left alone and the keeper takes it low, close to his ankles
short of length, angling in to Gambhir who goes back and tucks it straight to the square-leg fielder
length ball on off stump, 141 kph, Gambhir stays on the crease and drives it towards mid-on
short of length delivery outside off, Gambhir stays back and opens the face to run it down towards third-man for the first runs
short of length delivery, pitches outside legs and gets up on Rahane, he gets hit on the pads and the ball rolls towards square leg
good bounce by Irfan, the ball passes Rahane's bat but the slowness in the pitch means that the keeper takes it low
fuller length outside off, Gambhir comes forward tentatively, the ball takes an inside edge and hits his pads. The bowler appeals in vain.
fuller length angling in to Gambhir, he flicks it past square leg and the fine leg has to run around and make a sliding stop
back of length, cuts across a bit after pitching, but Rahane stays back and opens the face of the bat. The ball takes an outside edge but drops short of second slip
full delivery on the pads, Rahane is unable to get any bat on that, the ball hits the pads and rolls down fine for fine-leg fielder to field
beats him outside off with a full and wide delivery. Rahane is slow to come forward and then tries to drive it away from his body
beats him again with an angled delivery that pitches just short of good length and goes on with the angle. Rahane was playing a defensive shot, but played inside the line
length ball on off stump, doesn't bounce much, defended down the pitch by Gambhir
loses direction as this one drifts to the leg side, Gambhir easily deflects it to the fine-leg boundary
beaten outside off with one that bounces  extra and just cuts away from Gambhir. The batsman just hangs his bat at that one
fuller length on off, Gambhir doesn't commit fully to the front foot but drives it to wide mid-on for a single
length ball angling across, Rahane comes forward and defends it towards cover off the front foot
short of length outside off, Rahane stays back and opens the face at the last moment to run it down past a diving second-slip to the third-man boundary
length ball outside off, a teaser, but Gambhir doesn't take the bait and lets it go through to the keeper
another fuller length delivery outside off, Gambhir shoulders arms
brings it closer to the stumps this time and Gambhir comes forward to defend it to the off side
full delivery on the middle, and Gambhir gets a leading edge past cover as he closes the face of the bat to play it towards the leg side
short of length on the middle, the batsman hops back and dabs the ball to the left of the square-leg fielder
short of length delivery, hits the pads, and there is a loud appeal, but that pitched well outside the leg stump line
short of length delivery, close to off stump, Gambhir goes back and dabs it towards the right of point fielder for a single
another short of length delivery, on middle and leg, Rahane goes back and turns it to square leg

caught behind! Irfan strikes with a full delivery outside off, Rahane comes forward to drive it towards cover but the angle on the ball takes it across the batsman, it takes a faint edge to the keeper. Important strike by Irfan and Rahane loses another opportunity to impress
he gets a full delivery on the off and middle, and he obliges with a drive through midwicket with a lot of wrist for his first runs
short of length on the middle, defended back to the bowler
length ball on off, Kohli comes forward and pushes it to the gap at cover for a quick single
beats him outside off. Kohli stays in the crease to a length ball, expecting it to come back but the ball goes straight on
close shout for lbw! This one comes in after pitching on the middle, Kohli comes forward but plays outside the line this time, the ball however was going over the top of the stumps
and this one goes across after pitching on a length, Kohli is beaten again
short of length delivery on off stump, gives time to Kohli to see where this is going as he goes back and defends it towards the off side
down the leg side and it has been called a wide
short of length delivery, goes across the batsman. It pitches outside off and allows the batsman to leave that easily
some low bounce now. It was outside off, Kohli left it alone and Kamran is unable to make a clean stop as it bounces just before him
short of length, gets steep bounce with that. Gambhir hops and somehow defends it down on the pitch, off the shoulder of his bat
back of length outside off, Gambhir stays back and opens the face to play it towards point
bouncer this time. Gambhir ducks under it in time
another short of length delivery on the middle, Gambhir defends it towards midwicket on the hop
back of length delivery outside off, moves away after pitching, Gambhir lets it go
attempted short ball, but it is wide outside off and doesn't bounce much, Gambhir lets it go again
back of length, accurate on around the off stump line, Kohli defends it to the leg side
another short of length delivery, Kohli defend it off the back foot
he goes back to this back of length delivery on the middle and leg, and closes the face to run it down to fine leg

short of length delivery on the pads, Gambhir glances it down fine off the back foot, Umar Gul makes a diving save and almost gets Gambhir with a flat throw. A direct hit would have sent Gambhir back. Great fielding
beaten outside off! Gambhir stays back to a length ball and tries to play it down to third man. We can all picture it - he does that all the time
beaten again, not by hanging his bat, but this time as he comes to play a forward defence. The ball cuts away just enough to go past the bat
back of length delivery, around off stump, defended towards point off the back foot
he runs this down to third-man off the back foot as it is a short of a length delivery close to off stump
hits him high on the bat as he comes forward to defend this one

caught at point! Gambhir has given his wicket away playing a nothing shot. It was short. It was wide and instead of hitting it hard, he just guides it to the hands of point. He probably wanted to play that towards third-man, but the ball came a little slower and that messed up with his shot completely. Looked very bad.
attempts a yorker, but it is a low full-toss and Yuvraj just times it through point for his first runs
length ball on the pads, Yuvraj is quick to go back and flick it past square leg for another boundary
back of length on off stump, Kohli watches this closely as he defends it off the back foot towards the off side
beats him outside off, Kohli doesn't come forward to the length ball and plays inside the line. The ball carries on straight to the keeper

caught at second slip! the procession continues. Length ball, pitches on middle and goes across Kohli, who closes the face of the bat without either going forward or back, the ball takes an outside edge and flies low down to Younis at second-slip who completes a comfortable catch. India in deep mess again
short of length outside off, Raina stays back and seeing it's not close to him, shoulders arms
short ball cometh. Too high though and it's called a wide
length ball wide outside off, Raina comes forward positively and lets it go
fuller length on off stump, Raina takes a little step forward and punches it to mid-on
length ball on off stump, Yuvraj stays back when he should have been forward, the ball takes the outside edge and goes to third-man
back of length just outside off, Raina lets it go to the keeper
short of length delivery on off stump, Raina goes back and across and tucks it down to fine leg
short of length outside off, Yuvraj sways out of line
length ball outside off, Yuvraj stays on the crease and lifts his bat over his head to let it go
short of length closer to the stumps now, Yuvraj goes back and defends it towards point
length ball, pitches outside off, cuts in to the batsman, hits him on the thigh pad and goes through to the keeper. Junaid appeals, but its too high
short ball, doesn't get up too much, Raina goes back and across and gets on top of the bounce to play it down towards midwicket
back of length delivery outside off, Raina again goes back and across to defend it towards midwicket

another appeal for lbw, but it's high again. It nips back from a short of length. Raina stays back and tries to play it towards the leg side, gets hit on the thigh pad and the ball rolls towards third man
short of length ball on the middle, Yuvraj dabs it down to fine leg
fuller length outside off, Raina comes forward to defend it to the off side
short of length outside off, Yuvraj hops back and opens the face as he plays this away from his body, to run it down to third man
short of length ball, goes down the leg side with the angle, but that one was not very far from the leg stump as Raina had shuffled right across.
length ball outside off, he defends it from the crease towards point
now bring it closer to the off stump line, it is slightly short of length and Raina goes back to defend it back to the bowler
length ball on off, no forward stride from Raina as he defends this to the off side
short of length on off, defended towards the leg side
ooh, just went past the outside edge, on a good length and he drew Yuvraj forward, got it to move away and just go past the edge
on the stumps this time, angling towards off and middle and that's been defended into the off side
angling in towards middle and off and that's pushed into the off side from the crease
short of a good length and Yuvraj stays his ground and tries to crunch that past point, doesn't make contact, beats the edge again
shortish on middle, rocks on the back foot and knocks it down in front of the bowler
slower and shorter this time on the off stump, rocks back and knocks it down towards point, a maiden
dropped that short on middle, Raina rolled his wrists over that one and played it down to fine leg for a single
well timed by Yuvraj, just a punch and into the gap, short of a good length and he just eased it between mid-off and extra cover, quick outfield and it raced away
dropped that short outside off, thought of a pull but then withdrew, wide called for height
that's been bludgeoned, short outside off and he flat-bats that over the bowler's head, thwacked for a boundary
dropped short and that's been mistimed! Goes for the pull again but it goes off the bottom of the bat and lands just in front of mid-on
shortish and that's been punched through the covers for a couple, a deep point in place and he cuts that one off
no-ball, freehit coming, angling towards middle and leg and that's been tucked towards fine leg for a single
dispatched, what an expensive over, yields 18 runs, Gul goes round the wicket and drops it short, it's a slower ball and Raina seizes the length early to pull it over square leg
drifts on to the pads and Yuvraj turns it to the right of short fine leg
flighted on the middle, Raina takes his front foot out and drives it along the ground to long off
pushed through on off, defended towards midwicket
he misses out on runs as the ball thuds to the pads, while it was drifting down

and another one goes down, to a spinner this time. It was a flat and quick delivery, pitches on middle and off, and turns slightly. Yuvraj was on the back foot, trying to play it towards the on side but closed the face of the bat. The ball went past the outside edge to peg the off stick back. Yuvraj was completely squared up by that one
flighted delivery on off, defended towards midwicket
length ball angled across Raina, it is a bit wide outside off, Raina lets it go
fuller length on off, Raina plays it down towards mid-on with a straight bat
beats him now with one that goes on with the angle outside off, Raina stayed back and tried to pull his bat in at the last moment
length ball on off, defended towards cover off the front foot
short and angled across, Raina waits on the back foot and cracks it hard towards point where Umar Akmal makes a good stop
short of length on off, Raina defends it to point off the back foot. And that is a maiden over
flighted on off and middle, driven to Misbah at short midwicket
more flight, Dhoni comes forward and plays it towards Misbah at short midwicket
this one is flatter and turns in a bit, defended towards Misbah again
slightly quicker through the air, Dhoni punches it to long-on
flighted delivery, punched to mid-off off the front foot
length ball on off stump, Dhoni comes half forward and gets it down to third-man off the outside half of his bat
back of length delivery on off, Raina gets right behind that one as he defends it down the pitch
fuller length outside off, goes across Raina who doesn't take the bait, leaves it alone
another short of length ball on off, defended off the back foot
length ball outside off, Raina comes forward to drive it through off, but gets an inside edge towards deep midwicket
attempts a yorker, but Dhoni gets behind that one comfortably and guides it to deep square leg
fuller delivery on the middle, punched down the ground to long-on
drifts on to the pads, but Raina is not able to get it away
comes down the pitch and just punches it with a straight bat over long-on for a well-timed six
flighted delivery on the middle, driven back to the bowler
flatter delivery on off, punched to cover
goes back to this flatter delivery and punches it down the ground to long-off
short of length delivery on off, Raina stays in the crease and punches it to deep cover for a single
goes back to a short of length delivery on off, punches it past the cover fielder for a single
short ball outside off, Raina shapes for the pull, but decides in just placing the ball towards the leg side with a roll of wrists
stays back to this short of length delivery and tries to punch it through cover, gets an outside edge that runs down to third man
length ball on off, Raina takes his front foot out and times it over the in field at cover for a one-bounce four
slightly slower delivery on a length, allows Raina to get back and dab it towards midwicket for a quick single
flighted delivery on off, Raina comes forward and drives it to long-off
flatter delivery, Dhoni goes back and gets cramped for room, punches it back to the bowler
comes forward and turns this ball to square leg
tossed up delivery, pushed back to the bowler off the front foot
pushed to long-on off the back foot
driven to long-off off the fron foot for another easy single
flatter delivery on the middle stump, defended off the back foot
drifts on to the pads, Raina goes back and flicks it to deep backward square leg
comes forward to this flatter delivery and plays it towards midwicket with the turn
flighted delivery outside off, Dhoni pushes it to the left of cover fielder for a quick single
tossed up on the off stump line, pushed down the ground to long-on for another single
bowls a flat offspinner which is turned to the leg side off the back foot
on to the pads and Raina goes back to flick it towards deep backward square leg
comes down the track, but Hafeez pulls the length back, Dhoni has to defend
flatter delivery on off stump, Dhoni defends it towards midwicket
flatter and shorter, turns towards leg, Dhoni goes back and turns it to deep backward square
the ball just stops on Raina, who lobs it back towards the bowler, the bowler and short mid-on converge and it just falls short of both
flatter delivery outside off, defended to Younis at the short silly mid-on position
pushed through on off stump, defended to the off side
it spins down the leg side  and is called a wide
tossed up outside off, Dhoni comes forward and gets hit on the pads as he tries to push it towards the off side
quicker delivery outside off, Raina cuts it hard but straight to point
flighted on the off stump, Raina comes forward and pushes it to deep cover for a single
flat and quick on the off stump, Dhoni stays back to defend that to the leg side
tossed up on the middle and leg stump line, Dhoni turns it straight to the fielder at square leg
flatter delivery, punched back down the ground but Hafeez makes a good stop
another flat delivery on off stump, this time Raina punches it to deep cover
gets beaten as he goes for a cut outside off, the ball goes past the bottom edge
turns into Dhoni, who plays it to Misbah at midwicket
on the pads and it is dabbed towards square leg
flighted on off stump, turns in a bit, pushed to midwicket off the front foot
slower, outside off, Raina stays back and opens the face to play it towards point
tossed up on the middle, Raina comes forward to defend it back to the bowler
goes on the back foot and punches it through cover for a single
pushed through on the middle stump line, defended back to the bowler
tosses it up outside off, Dhoni comes forward and drives it straight to cover
more flight and it's full too, driven hard but straight to mid-off who is up
shimmies down the track but has to defend as the length is not there
flat and quick, punched straight to extra cover off the back foot
goes back and closes the face of the bat to play it on the leg side, takes off for a quick single
bowls it flat and quick, but it is down the leg side
comes down the pitch and picks this one up from the middle stump line and launches it to the deep midwicket boundary. Where did that comes from?
and another one, this time the ball is fuller and it allows him to get under it better as he strikes this over wide long-on
flighted delivery on off, defended back to the bowler
flighted delivery on off, defended to the off side
tosses it up on off, the ball turns a bit and Raina defends it off the front foot
quick and full outside off, punched back to the bowler

follows the quicker one with a tossed up delivery on the middle stump, Raina thrusts his pad out towards the off and plays outside the line, the ball hits him on the front pad and the umpire raises his finger. Raina falls after a useful stand of 48 with Dhoni

first baller for Ashwin! The wheels are coming off. It was flatter, quicker and it spins in to Ashwin. The batsman stayed on the crease as he tried to play that to the leg side, gets hit on the back pad in front of off. Ajmal on a roll again.
tossed up delivery on off, Jadeja comes forward to smother that
he is decided no point playing the waiting game, he comes down the track and smashes it to deep midwicket boundary, into the stands
flatter delivery, pushed toward long-on for a single
flatter delivery on off, Jadeja comes forward to defend
flighted delivery on off, pushed back to the bowler
pushed through outside off, Jadeja comes forward to defend that  to off side
on the middle, Jadeja turns it to the leg side and wants a single, Dhoni sends him back rightly
flatter delivery, turns into Dhoni, who pushes it back to the bowler
flatter and quicker, but turning down the leg side, hits the pads
the top spinner, it is quicker on the middle, Dhoni defends that off the back foot
the doosra now, Dhoni spots it and thrusts his front foot out to defend that
short, but quick, the batsman goes back and places it past point for a single
the straighter one, Jadeja plays outside the line expecting it to turn, luckily for him, the ball was outside off
flatter delivery on the middle stump, defended off the back foot
an appeal for caught behind down the leg side, the umpire says no and calls it a wide. It was short and flat outside leg, Dhoni tries to play it with a vertical bat but misses.

that, sir, is a good stop. It would be harsh to call it a drop. It was flighted on off and Dhoni smashed it flat back to the left of the bowler, who stuck his hand out and now he seems to to have done some damage. The physio is out. Sometimes it doesn't help if the reflex takes you towards the ball rather than away from it. It must have stung in this cold. That hit his left-hand thumb
flatter and quicker on the middle and leg, defended back to the bowler
slightly short on the pads, Dhoni goes back and places it to deep midwicket
fligthed on the off, Jadeja comes forward and manages some bat as he tries to defend off the front foot, ball goes towards square leg
goes back to one on the leg stump, flicked to deep backward square
accurate ball to start with, on off stump, it is pushed back to the bowler
short of length on the off and middle, comes back in a touch, Dhoni gets an inside edge on to his pads
this one holds its line and beats Dhoni as he comes forward, a little late, to try and push that towards the off side
comes down the track, but Gul fires it on the pads, Dhoni flicks it to deep square leg for a single
length ball on middle and off, Jadeja defends it back to the bowler
back of length outside off, Jadeja opens the face to run it down to third man
full and flat, flicked past midwicket for a couple
flighted on off, Jadeja pushes it to the right of midwicket
flatter and quicker, again defended off the front foot
quicker delivery, hits the pads as Jadeja tries to flick, the bowler appeals, but that was just missing leg
flatter delivery on the stumps, punched to cover off the back foot
slow, outside off, Jadeja shapes to play a cut, but can't get any timing as he ends up playing that straight to point
length ball on off, Dhoni unleashes a booming drive on the up but can't beat extra cover
attempts a yorker, but it ends up being a low full-toss, Dhoni takes a step down the pitch and flicks it past short fine leg
short of length on off, Dhoni dabs it straight to point

caught at point! short and not much room, Dhoni goes for the aerial cut but it goes straight to the hands of Umar Akmal at point. Dhoni falls for the first time in this series and that wicket could be the difference between a 200-run total to a 150 one now.
length ball on off, Bhuvi comes forward to push it to cover
length ball outside off, left alone by the batsman
flighted delivery on off and middle, Jadeja comes forward in defence
tossed up and full, driven to midwicket off the front foot
flatter delivery on off, defended back down the pitch again
sees the flight and lofts it straight down the ground, where Junaid from long-on runs around to make a good stop
flatter delivery, defended towards the leg side
another delivery pushed through on off, Jadeja defends that to the off side
short of length outside off, defended by Bhuvi towards point
bowls it full and straight, swings in a bit, batsman gets hit on the pads and bowler appeals, but that was just going down the leg side
full ball outside off, driven straight to cover off the front foot

dropped. It was short outside off and Bhuvi gets a thick edge that goes between keeper and first slip. But Kamran went for it, didn't get a hand, and blinds the first slip fielder. What more, the ball rolls to touch the helmet behind the keeper
a fast yorker, dug out on the leg side for a single
short of length delivery, defended back to the bowler
flat and short on off stump, punched to wide mid-off
flighted delivery on off, turned to midwicket off the front foot
more flight from Ajmal, Jadeja pushes it down to long-on
flat and quick on the stumps, defended off the back foot
that was the doosra! It pitched on the middle and leg and was expecting it to turn it down leg, but it straightened and hit him on the front pad as Bhuvi was looking to turn it to square leg.
it is the flighted off spinnner outside off, Ishant does well to defend that off the front foot
that has gone over the sight screen to the second tier. Jadeja jumps out of the crease, makes room and just picks this one up from length. That came from nowhere
length ball, down the leg side and is called a wide, a bit harshly
back of length delivery on off, Jadeja opens the face and runs it down to the left of the keeper, who makes a half stop
short of length delivery on off stump, cut straight to point
stays back to a length ball and defends it to cover
full yorker, but drifting down the leg side, Ishant digs it out
short of length outside off, Ishant lets it go through to the keeper
flighted delivery on off stump, turned to deep midwicket for a single
off spinning delivery outside off, Ishant punches it to cover
tossed up delivery, the top spinner, on off stump line, defended off the front foot
flat and fast off spinner, Ishant punches it back to the bowler
another quicker on, Ishant pushes it to cover off the back foot
slow, short and outside off, Ishant loses his timing and is not able to get it away
full ball outside off, Jadeja drives it without much timing to extra cover
it's a full and fast yoker, misses the bat and the stumps as it goes past the leg stump to the keeper
attempts another yorker, but it's a low full-toss which Jadeja drives past a diving midwicket to the cow corner, for a couple
another low full-toss, it's hit straight down the ground where Umar Gul, from long-on, comes around to make a sliding stop
length ball, angled into the pads, Jadeja misses his flick and the ball thuds into the pad. It was going down the leg side
short ball, slightly slower, Jadeja cuts it but is not able to beat Umar Akmal at point
flighted delivery, Ishant clubs it over mid-off to get his first runs
pushed through on the middle stump line, defended back to the bowler
flat and quick on the leg stump line, punched to mid-off
fuller down the leg side, Ishant chips it down the ground and the long-on fielder fields it on the bounce
full and flighted, driven to deep midwicket for a single
Ishant drives it straight back to the bowler! It was a tame shot and Ajmal got his right hand to it, fumbled but caught it on the second try. It's Ajmal's fourth
drives this full ball hard, back to the bowler who gets hit on the boots and deflects it to long-off
short of length, defended towards point
fuller length delivery on off, Shami opens the face to play it towards point
a good bouncer to the No. 11, it follows the batsman who arches back to sway out of the line
length ball outside off, this one holds its line and Shami is beaten outside off as he tries to play that from his crease
a quick full-toss, Shami throws his bat at it, gets a faint edge, but the ball just goes past the off stump on its way to the keeper
flighted delivery on off, Jadeja launches this over cow corner into the stands
flatter delivery, angled in, defended off the front foot
full and fast on the middle stump, defended back to the bowler

caught at long-on! Ajmal completes five as Jadeja tries to send this one out of the ground, only manages to get it as far as long-on. A comforatble catch by Umar Akmal and Ajmal is pumped after that wicket.

inn2.comm: angles it across the left-handed Jamshed, a bit wide outside off, left alone
swings it away from the left-hander, but it's bit too wide and is left alone
on the pads and Jamshed times it past midwicket for a couple
on the pads again, Jamshed waits and flicks it down to fine-leg
short of length outside off, Akmal comes forward and opens the face, but Kohli at point makes a good stop
outswinger goes past the outside edge
short of length wide outside off, cuts away from the batsman and he pulls in the bat at the last moment
length ball outside off, 136 kph, left alone by the batsman, Dhoni takes it low
another one outside off, a bit wide, left alone by the batsman
loose shot by Jamshed as he hangs his bat at a length ball wide outside off, gets beaten
keeps it in that channel outside off, Jamshed thinks about playing at that one, but leaves it alone in the end
beaten by a slower ball, it was on length outside off and Jamshed came forward to play at that one, it slightly left the batsman to go past the outside edge

and he strikes with that one that comes booming in from outside off.  We have seen it already a few times in this series, Akmal gets stuck on the crease and he is right in front of the stumps. Bhuvneshwar continues to impress with his swing
bowls a short of length delivery wide outside off, Younis plays it away from his body, straight to point
not much swing on this one. It angles in from wide outside off and Younis Khan defends it off the back foot
short ball outside off, it sails over the head of the batsman, called a wide
short of length, comes in with the angle, Younis hops and defends it to midwicket
short of length outside off, some width too and Younis gets on top of the bounce and punches it with a lot of timing through square on off side
back of length outside off, Younis stays back and defends it towards the off side
length ball outside off, comes in with the angle, defended down the pitch
on a length again, angling in from wide of the crease, defended off the back foot
fuller delivery wide outside off, Jamshed crunches it though cover, but Rahane makes a flying stop at that position preventing a certain boundary
short of length on off and middle, Jamshed wanted to play that on the leg side, but gets an inside edge on to his pads
length delivery on the pads, now Jamshed times it to the leg side and Jadeja makes an excellent save at midwicket
that kept low outside off, it was short of length and goes under the bat as Jamshed tries to play that away from his body
cuts away after pitching short of length outside off, beats Younis Khan in his defence
pitches it further up, outside off, Younis comes forward to defend it to point
angles in from wide off the crease, Younis gets an inside edge as he tries to turn it to the leg side
short of length outside off, Younis stays back and punches it to wide mid-on for a single
he takes a step down to make room outside off, cuts this short of length delivery but point makes a diving stop
now he beats Jamshed as the ball leaves the batsman after angling it in
bowls it slightly fuller a touch outside off, shapes away a bit but Younis pushes it to wide mid-off for a single
short of length on the stumps, defended off the back foot
another accurate delivery on the stumps, Jamshed defends it down to mid-on
fuller length outside off, Jamshed punches it seemingly in the gap, but Rahane makes another one-handed diving stop
attempts a short ball, but Jamshed plays that shot very well, he gets into a position quickly and pulls it to the square leg boundary easily
length ball outside off, Jamshed stays in his crease as he pushes this one to cover
short of length outside off, Younis plays that with an open face, it goes straight to point
punched off the back foot to mid-on off a back of a length delivery
bowls it a touch fuller, the ball comes in a bit and Younis gets an inside edge to the leg side as he tries to push this one to the off
another excellent save at point, this time by Kohli. Younis stretched out to square drive this widish delivery but fails to beat the man

the middle stump has been flattened! Not a big inswinger, but enough on that to take the inside edge as Younis comes forward to play a loose drive towards cover. And just like that, Pakistan are two down
length ball outside off, Misbah lets it go
play and a miss outside off. It was a length ball, touch wide outside off, Jamshed tries to play it through covers, but away from the body, the ball goes past the outside edge
some bounce for Shami from back of length now. Jamshed pulls his bat in at the last moment
cuts into Jamshed after pitching, he gets hit on the thigh pad as he tries to flick it to the on side
back of length outside off, Jamshed defends it off the back foot
short of length outside off, Jamshed wanted to wrist it towards the leg side but gets a leading edge back to the bowler, safe though
length ball closing in on off stump, Jamshed defends it solidly towards off
edges and it fall just short of the second slip. It moves away as Misbah tries to defend that. But well played by Misbah who played that with soft hands
short of length, goes straight on, defended off the back foot
short of length outside off, Misbah defends, but gets an inside edge on to his pads
pitches this one a bit further, Misbah comes forward to defend and gets an inside edge to fine-leg
bowls length wide outside off, Jamshed stays patient and lets it go
length ball outside off, Jamshed gets solidly behind that to defend it to the off side
bowls on a length on off stump, goes straight on, Misbah defends off the front foot
gets a slight shape going away from the batsman, Misbah plays it down to third man
short of length on off stump line, Jamshed punches it to mid-on off the back foot
slightly short in length and Jamshed rocks into a good position and pulls it hard in front of square for a handsome shot
bowls it full and Jamshed, who was waiting on the back foot, gets an inside edge down to fine leg for a couple
back of length outside off, Jamshed stays compact and defends it to the off side
swings it in  from wide outside off, Misbah leaves it alone, but that had come in by some distance
goes straight on after pitching short of length, Misbah lets it go through
he pulls out the bat at the last moment, as the ball doesn't come in and goes straight on
length ball outside off, not much movement, Misbah gets right behind this one in defence
fuller length, wide outside off, it's left alone by the batsman
comes in after pitching short of length, Misbah gets behind that and punches it to mid-on
starts off with a length ball on off, Jamshed stays back and plays it towards point off the outside half of his bat
short of length on off, Jamshed plays it late and closes the face to turn it to deep backward square
back of length outside off, Misbah stays patient and lets it go through
fuller length on off stump, Misbah tries to turn it to the leg side but there is a fielder close on the leg side - short square leg the tv commentator call him
short of length and bounces ideally for Misbah to chop it down past point for a couple
back of length, angled across Jamshed, who plays a back foot punch to the off side, but it's hit straight to point
keeps it in the channel outside off, Misbah comes forward to defend but gets an inside edge to the leg side
tries a fuller length, but Misbah just times it straight down the ground for a beautifully hit boundary. Everything right about that
he pulls the length back again and Misbah lets it go as it is wide outside off
short of length, comes in after pitching, Misbah gets an inside edge as he tries to defend that
length ball outside off, Misbah covers the line of the stumps and lets it go to the keeper
keeps it outside off, Misbah keeps being patient
bowls it a touch short of good length, Jamshed steers it down to third-man off the back foot
beats Misbah with one bowled with a scrambled seam. Misbah hung is bat loosely at that one
tries to play a forceful shot of a length ball wide outside off, gets beaten again
bowls it closer to the stumps, the batsman gets behind it to defend it down the pitch
gets some width and it is short of length too, crunches it to the off side but is not able to beat Kohli at point
length ball on off stump, slightly slower, the batsman stays in the crease and defends
short of length, but drifting down the pads and Jamshed flicks it fine. Shami runs around from deep backward square and stops it with his boot
angling in from round the wicket, Jamshed turns it to midwicket for a single
fuller length outside off, Misbah comes forward to drive and gets an inside edge
short of length, angles in towards the pads, Misbah runs it down the deep backward square leg for a single
short of length, angling away, punched to cover off the back foot
bowls it slightly fuller and Jamshed tries to flay at it from the crease, gets a thick outside edge that flies through to the third-man boundary
length ball, angled in from wide outside off, Misbah times is through square leg for a boundary.
back of length on off stump, Misbah goes back and across and defends it towards the leg side
short of length outside off, Misbah stays back and punches it square on the off side, Kohli gets a hand to keep it to a single
he gets an inside edge as he tries to whip this short of length delivery coming in with the angle from round the stumps
that misses the off stump by  a whisker. It cuts in after pitching outside off, from round the wicket, and Jamshed played a loose shot away from his body
quick single taken as Jamshed drops the ball on the leg side off the back foot
short ball on off stump, Jamshed gets on top of the bounce and plays it down to third man
short of length on off stump, Misbah gets an inside edge on to his pads as he tries to punch it towards off
another short of length delivery, loses pace after pitching, Misbah defends it back to the bowler
keeps it outside off and it goes through to the keeper, left alone by Misbah
he bowls the second full delivery and Misbah takes advantage of it a second time, places it beautifully through the gap at cover
beaten outside off with with a short of length delivery
bowls a fuller length outside off and beats Jamshed as he tries to drive without any feet movement
angles in from round the wicket, Jamshed stays back and plays it late towards fine leg
holds its line after pitching outside off, beats Misbah as he comes forward to defend
short of length outside off, takes the outside edge to third-man
short of length outside off, the ball comes in with the angle and then cuts away, beats Jamshed in his defence
fuller length on the middle stump line, Jamshed tries to play it to on side, but gets a leading edge towards third man
short of length outside off, Jamshed gets behind that one to defend it to off side
swings away from the left-hander and beats his defensive prod
keeps it tight on the stumps, Jamshed plays it off the back foot, back to the bowler
defends this to off side as Bhuvneshwar sticks to his short of length business
he attempts his third fuller delivery, and it's a third time he his hit for the boundary, this time by Jamshed, beautifully through cover
back of length now, defended to mid-on
he plays it with soft hands towards mid-on and takes off for a quick single
short of length from round the wicket, Jamshed chops it down to second slip
this one is bowled on off stump line, short of length, defended down the pitch
it was beautifully timed to the off side off a length delivery, but Jadeja dives and cuts it off
fuller length, the batsman punches it to mid-off without moving his feet at all
more back foot defence from Jamshed off a short of length delivery outside off
flatter delivery on off stump, Misbah goes back and turns it past square leg for a single
slightly shorter on off stump and Jamshed quickly goes back and punches it past wide mid-on for a boundary

picks up the wrong shot. It was a flighted delivery on the off and middle, Jamshed chooses to play a premeditated sweep and is struck on the front pad. Ashwin lets out a cry of excitement immediately and the decision is given. That is a huge wicket considering how Jamshed has played this series
big spin after pitching on middle, Dhoni is not able to cover that and it goes down to the fine-leg boundary for five wides
tossed up outside off, Umar takes a big stride and pushes it on to the gap at cover for a single
another tossed up delivery outside off, Misbah takes a forward stride and places it on off side for a single
more spin for Ashwin, this time it hits the pads and goes to backward square leg
bowls it full on the pads and that is easy picking for Misbah, who plays it late and times it to the deep square leg boundary
fuller length outside off stump, Misbah defends off the front foot
back of length, angling in to the batsman, who plays a back foot defence
fuller length outside off, Misbah comes forward but the ball takes an outside edge, it doesn't carry to the fielder at first slip. Ashwin is standing at first slip.
short of length outside off, left alone by the batsman
back of length outside off, defended towards the off side
flighted ball outside off, Umar defends but there was a minor hesitation as the batsman wanted a single. Rightly sent back
tossed up delivery on off and middle, it spins in and hits the pads
he goes back and pushes it to mid-on but Raina cuts it off from midwicket with a diving stop
tossed up delivery, driven back to the bowler
flighted outside off stump, Umar Akmal this times drives it to deep cover off the front foot
tosses it up outside off, Misbah doesn't try to push that too hard, places that to deep cover
flatter delivery on off stump, defended by Misbah
gives the ball some air now, Misbah comes forward and drives it down to long-off
flatter on off stump, punched back to the bowler off the back foot
fuller this time, it is driven back to the bowler again
gets some width this time, he stretches out and pushes it to deep cover
was that an outside edge going down? Possibly. It gripped the surface and turned past Misbah forward defence, and Dhoni puts down a tough one.
tossed up outside off, Umar comes down a couple of steps to smother the spin
full and flighted  on off, driven to long-on for a single
more flight on off stump, Misbah turns it to fine leg for a single
similar delivery, different method as Umar drives it down to long-on
and it's through Dhoni again. It turns down the leg side and goes between Dhoni's legs for more extras
flighted delivery outside off, Misbah drives it easily to deep cover
flatter outside off, Umar takes a couple of steps down, but is not to the pitch of the ball, defends it back to the bowler
full tossed up delivery, defended off the front foot to cover
gets some width with a flighted delivery, and he slices it to deep point
flatter delivery on off, Umar takes a big stride and defends it back down the pitch
it is slightly short this time, allows Umar to go back and push it past cover for a single
some turn and bounce for Jadeja now, beats Misbah in his back foot defence
front foot defence on a flatter delivery
fuller delivery on the middle, defended to midwicket
slow and flighted on off, Umar pushes it to cover off the front foot
on the pads and its is easily turned over to fine-leg for a single
flighted delivery outside off, Misbah defends on front foot
he turns it to midwicket off a delivery on middle stump
loses direction as this one goes down the leg side
tossed up on off stump, Misbah drives it to long-on off the front foot
flatter and quicker outside off, defended towards cover off the back foot
slightlly slower, defended off the front foot this time
floats it up further, Misbah gets an inside edge to square leg as he tries to drive it to the off side
driven straight to cover off the front foot
on the middle stump line, defended towards the off side
width outside off and Umar unleashes a cracking cover drive past a diving Raina
flighted on the middle stump, defended off the front foot
pushes it full and flat on off, Misbah comes forward to drive it down to long-on
more flight outside off, driven to cover off the front foot
he shows more patience as he defends this fuller ball back to the bowler
turned to midwicket off the back foot
short of length outside off, cut hard, but straight to point
front foot solid defence by Misbah to a flatter delivery
stays in the crease and defends again
pitches further up and Misbah drives it past cover for a single
turn and bounce outside off, Umar stays on top and cuts it to point
and again bounces extra, Umar plays it to the left of point
fuller length on off stump, defended off the front foot
flighted delivery on the stump, Misbah turns it to deep square leg easily for a single
full and flighted on off, Umar drives it hard back to the bowler, who gets a hand to it
a full-toss this time, Misbah aims for the gap at deep midwicket with a gentle drive but the fielder at wide long on cuts it off
turned to fine-leg for a couple of runs
flatter and quicker on middle stump, defended back to the bowler
flighted on the leg stump, played back to the bowler
tossed up delivery on off, defended towards off
full outside off, Misbah squeezes it to point
flatter delivery on off, the batsman takes a big stride to defend that
he gets some turn and bounce, it takes an outside edge but falls safely in the off side
it is the slider this time and Misbah gets hit on the pads, outside the line of off though
complete a maiden with a quick delivery on off that is defended by Misbah
gets a nice full-toss outside off  and Umar says thank you and crashes it through extra cover for a boundary
flighted and slow, Umar goes for the sweep and misses, the bowler appeals for lbw, but the impact was outside leg stump
flighted delivery outside off, Umar tries to drive it hard, but is not to the pitch of the ball, and has to defend
this time he gets everything in that sweep shot. It was outside leg stump and Umar swept it powerfully through deep backward square leg
flatter and on the middle, Umar cuts it late, straight to point
flighted delivery on the middle, defended off the front foot
flighted outside off, Misbah drives it straight to cover
flatter delivery, dips, grips and bounces big time, beats Misbah's forward prod
on to the pads and Misbah turns it to deep square leg for a couple to bring up the fifty of the partnerhship
flighted outside off, driven to deep cover for an easy single
he tries to cut a ball that is not short enough, plays it to point
fuller delivery, defended off the front foot

and that leg slip finally comes into the picture. Ashwin has been bowling from round the wicket all day. This one pitches on the leg stump and Misbah glides it straight into the hands of Rahane at that position. Some joy for the India team finally
flighted outside off, turns into the batsman who defends it off the back foot
it's full and Shoaib tries to flick it on leg, but gets a leading edge back down the pitch
tossed up outside off, the batsman takes a step down and defends to off side
flatter and shorter, comes in after pitching, defended off the back foot
bowls a slider this time, it goes across Shoaib who gets beaten outside off
width provided outside off, Umar cuts it hard but that is stopped well by a diving point fielder
flatter outside off, defends it to the off side
tossed up delivery, driven straight to cover
it is a quick slider again, hits the gloves as Shoaib tries to cut it
fuller and flatter, the batsman chips it over the infield to deep cover
short of length outside off and Shoaib takes the full advantage to cut it past point for a boundary.
fuller length delivery on off, defended back to the bowler

cuts in sharply after pitching on length and hits the pad first, then the bat, as Shoaib Malik tried to defend that off the front foot. He didn't really take a good forward stride on that one, and was beaten by the movement off the pitch. Replays show that the impact was marginally outside the line of off stump, but that looked close the moment he was struck. Slightly unlucky Shoaib
length ball outside off, Hafeez takes a forward stride and defends it back down the pitch
fuller length outside off, draws an outside edge that goes to third-man. A slip is in place too
shuffles across to play this length delivery to midwicket, a sharp Rahane cuts across to have a shy at the stumps
tossed up delivery on off, defended to the off side
more flight, on the middle stump line, defended to midwicket this time
bowls this slider which takes an inside edge and goes to short fine leg
flatter delivery on the pads, the batsman is not able to get it away
he takes his chance as he tries to slog is out of the ground, but it takes a top-edge which lands safely at deep midwicket as fielders are in.
flatter delivery on the stumps, defended off the front foot to the off side
fuller length outside off, Hafeez slices it towards point where Kohli makes a diving stop to prevent runs
length ball outside off, the batsman covers the line of stumps and lets it go through to the keeper
fuller length, but it is on the pads and the batsman has it easy as he flicks it down to fine leg for a single
short of length outside off, Umar drops it down to the off side and looks for a single, but is rightly sent back by Hafeez
length ball outside off, punched back to the bowler off the front foot
another fuller length delivery just outside off, Umar drives it straight to mid-off
makes room and tries to send this over extra cover, but mistimes it, goes on the bounce to long-on

he charges out and is stumped by a mile! He gave away the trick too early and Jadeja altered his length by dropping it short. Realising that he was no where near the pitch of the delivery, he tried to defend it, but the ball squeezed through the gap between the bat and pad and Dhoni completed the stumping in a flash
bowls it flat and quick, defended off the front foot
gets it to turn past the outside edge now, beats Gul outside off
slower this time, but Gul stays watchful, defends it back down the pitch
slightly fuller, defended to the leg side this time
short of length delivery on off stump, it takes an outside edge that runs down to third man
short and quick delivery outside off, Gul gets beaten on the cut as it bounces a touch extra
short of length outside off again, Gul watches this one go through to the keeper
another short of length delivery on off stump, Gul chops it on the off side
length ball on off, Gul pulls out a fantastic front foot shot from his hat, just times it through the gap at cover and the fielders had no chance
short of length outside off, left alone by the batsman
on to the pads, turns in a bit and it falls just short of Rahane at leg slip as Hafeez closed the face of the bat
on to the pads, Gul stays back and steers it easily to fine leg
tossed up on the middle, takes a leading edge towards cover as he tries to defend
on the pads, Gul plays it towards square leg with the turn
was that a drop! Hafeez played a premeditated sweep off a fuller delivery, that went straight to Rahane at leg slip who fluffed it, the ball was around chest high
takes a forward stride and defends it towards midwicket
short of length delivery on off, defended towards mid-on
short ball on off stump, Gul gets on top of the bounce and defends it to the off side
short of length delivery outside off, cut straight to point
back of length delivery outside off, Gul cuts it past point this time and Ashwin at third-man was always slow. A faster fielder could have cut it off.
back of a length, pushed to cover off the back foot
short ball, on the middle stump, doesn't get too high and hits Gul on the helmet. The batsman had taken his eyes off the ball and it smacked him on the side
flighted delivery on off, the batsman takes a forward stride and plays it to off with an open face for a single
fuller delivery outside off, driven back to the bowler
more flight, it is on the off stump line, Gul drives it to deep midwicket
pushes this one through outside off, the batsman steers it to deep point for a single
lets out a loud appeal.. It was the carrom ball, it pitches outside off and hit the back pad in line, but that was probably a little high. Marginal I would say.
fuller delivery, defended off the front foot
length ball outside off, Hafeez comes forward and plays it with an open face, straight to point though
width provided with a fuller delivery outside off, it is driven past point and Ishant makes a sliding stop at the boundary to keep the batsmen to two
back of length on off stump, defended towards off side and Hafeez wanted a single. He was rightly sent back and Kohli was on to the ball in a flash
short of length on off stump, pushed back to the bowler off the back foot
keeps it tight on the stumps, the ball takes a leading edge and Kohli makes another good save at point
finishes a good over with a length delivery on the stumps, Hafeez pushed it back to the bowler
bowls it flat with a slightly round-arm action, defended to off
keeps it tight on off, defended to the leg side this time
flat and short, quick too, pushed straight to midwicket
full and quick, defended back to the bowler
quicker delivery on the pads, hits the batsman and rolls to short fine leg
gets turn, gets bounce and beats Hafeez outside off
short of length, accurately on off stump, punched back to the bowler

caught at long on! Umar Gul cracks under pressure. The shot was on as it was a length ball on off stump, Gul took a swing at that one but wasn't able to time it very well, the ball settles into the hands of Jadeja at long-on.
short of length ball on off stump, defended to the off side
short-ish delivery, Ajmal tries to play the pull on one-leg, but gets hit on the body and the ball rolls on the off side. The two take a single
slower delivery on off stump, the batsman has to hold his shot back and he only manages to play it back to the bowler
short of length with lot of width, Hafeez tries to cut it hard but gets beaten by that one.
length ball outside off, gets some away movement at 7.30 pm in the evening, beats the outside edge as Ajmal tries to cut it

and this time he manages to get an edge. It was a similar delivery outside off as the last one, Ajmal tried to run it down to third-man with a horizontal bat and ended up playing at the ball away from his body. The ball takes an edge and it's an easy catch for Dhoni. First wicket for Shami Ahmed in ODIs, 200th catch for Dhoni

he is just run himself out! Although Raina's stop at cover had a fair bit to do with that. Junaid tapped it to the off side and took off immediately, Raina dived and made a half stop. Luckily for him, the ball didn't go to far. He took the ball, realised that there was complete communication breakdown between the batsmen with both on one end, aims and takes down the stumps at striker's end direct. Dhoni was there too had he missed.
fuller length outside off, driven to mid-off
short of length outside off, leaves the batsman too, left alone by the batsman
another full delivery completes a maiden over - Shami's fourth - as Irfan blocks it out to the off side
fuller length delivery on the off, driven hard to mid-off where Raina misfields, but the batsmen don't take the single
he goes into the position to play the scoop and that 's disturbs Ishant's concentration, he bowls it wide outside off
he makes room outside off and slices the length delivery over point for a one-bounce four
short slower ball, he pulls it hard and beats the midwicket fielder. The fielder at wide long-on does the clean-up job
length ball outside off, and Hafeez is doing all by himself. Just blasts this over extra cover with plenty of timing, it almost carried over the ropes.

Drama!! It's a chest high full-toss which Hafeez manages to play to short fine leg. But there was no run, but Irfan had run all the way to the other end. The throw came to Ishant's end and he had all the time to collect and run the batsman out. But he is not next to the stumps and misses completely

caught at midwicket! Hafeez has hit this length ball straight to Yuvraj at midwicket. It wasn't a free-hit as the last ball was no-ball for height. But Pakistan have imploded big time here. Yuvraj runs around the outfield, slides on the field, he gets surrounded by his teammates.
